      <title>曾预测韩国央行降息的经济学家认为未来将进一步放松货币政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-28/economist-who-predicted-bok-cut-sees-more-easing-ahead-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为数不多的正确预测韩国央行周四降息的经济学家之一认为，未来政策将进一步放松，并表示明年基准利率可能降至 2.25%。野村控股经济学家 Jeong Woo Park 在“彭博：中国秀”上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-28/economist-who-predicted-bok-cut-sees-more-easing-ahead-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 03:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉评级：中国房地产市场低迷或将延续至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/china-s-property-slump-may-extend-into-2025-fitch-ratings-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级表示，尽管政府推出刺激措施刺激需求，但房价和销售依然疲软，中国持续多年的房地产危机将持续到 2025 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/china-s-property-slump-may-extend-into-2025-fitch-ratings-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 03:18:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
